interfaces.label: CloudBasicUrls
description: Represents basic URLs for the Cloud plugin, that do not require specific user roles to access.

children.label: baseUrl
description: This is the URL of the Cloud interface.

children.label: kibanaUrl
description: The full URL to the Kibana deployment.

children.label: deploymentsUrl
description: This is the path to the Cloud deployments management page. The value is already prepended with `baseUrl`.

children.label: deploymentUrl
description: This is the path to the Cloud deployment management page for the deployment to which the Kibana instance belongs. The value is already prepended with `baseUrl`.

children.label: profileUrl
description: The full URL to the user profile page on Elastic Cloud. Undefined if not running on Cloud.

children.label: organizationUrl
description: The full URL to the organization management page on Elastic Cloud. Undefined if not running on Cloud.

children.label: performanceUrl
description: The full URL to the performance page on Elastic Cloud. Undefined if not running on Cloud.

children.label: usersAndRolesUrl
description: The full URL to the users and roles page on Elastic Cloud. Undefined if not running on Cloud.

children.label: projectsUrl
description: The full URL to the serverless projects page on Elastic Cloud. Undefined if not running in Serverless.

children.label: snapshotsUrl
description: This is the path to the Snapshots page for the deployment to which the Kibana instance belongs. The value is already prepended with `deploymentUrl`.

children.label: serverless
signature: { project_id: string; project_name?: string | undefined; project_type?: "search" | "security" | "observability" | "workplaceai" | undefined; product_tier?: "complete" | "logs_essentials" | "essentials" | "search_ai_lake" | undefined; orchestrator_target?: string | undefined; in_trial?: boolean | undefined; } | undefined
